ttp_template:
<group name="auto_commit_backup_release_commit_timeout_primary_release">
  software releases in {{RELEASE_LOCATION | ORPHRASE}}
{{BACKUP_RELEASE | ORPHRASE}} (Backup Release)
{{PRIMARY_RELEASE | ORPHRASE}} (Primary Release)
Auto Commit  : {{AUTO_COMMIT | ORPHRASE}}
Commit Timeout  : {{COMMIT_TIMEOUT | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
textfsm_template:
Value RELEASE_LOCATION (\S+)
Value BACKUP_RELEASE (\S+)
Value PRIMARY_RELEASE (\S+)
Value AUTO_COMMIT (\S+)
Value COMMIT_TIMEOUT (.*\w)

Start
  ^==+
  ^\s+software releases in ${RELEASE_LOCATION}
  ^${BACKUP_RELEASE}\s+\(Backup Release\)
  ^${PRIMARY_RELEASE}\s+\(Primary Release\)
  ^Auto Commit\s+:\s+${AUTO_COMMIT}
  ^Commit Timeout\s+:\s+${COMMIT_TIMEOUT}

Done
